            <p><div class="content_para"><p>This is the current release of the guideline.</p>
<p>This guideline updates a previous version: VA/DoD clinical practice guideline for management of substance use disorders (SUD). Washington (DC): Department of Veteran Affairs, Department of Defense; 2009 Aug. 158 p.</p>
<p>This guideline meets NGC's 2013 (revised) inclusion criteria.</p></div></p>
