                    <h4>UMLS Concepts <a href="/web/20180712193938/https://www.guideline.gov/help-and-about/search-browse/umls-concepts" class="what-is">(what is this?)</a></h4>
                <div class="field">
                    <h5 class="field-label">ICD9CM</h5>
                    <div class="field-content">
<a href="/web/20180712193938/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0236663&amp;fLockTerm=Alcohol+withdrawal">Alcohol withdrawal</a>
 (291.81), <a href="/web/20180712193938/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0001957&amp;fLockTerm=Alcohol+withdrawal+delirium">Alcohol withdrawal delirium</a>
 (291.0), <a href="/web/20180712193938/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0004933&amp;fLockTerm=Behavior+therapy">Behavior therapy</a>
 (94.33), <a href="/web/20180712193938/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0152128&amp;fLockTerm=Drug+withdrawal">Drug withdrawal</a>
 (292.0), <a href="/web/20180712193938/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0154474&amp;fLockTerm=Other+and+unspecified+alcohol+dependence%2c+unspecified">Other and unspecified alcohol dependence, unspecified</a>
 (303.90), <a href="/web/20180712193938/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0178056&amp;fLockTerm=Psychiatric+mental+status+determination">Psychiatric mental status determination</a>
 (94.11), <a href="/web/20180712193938/https://www.guideline.gov/search?f_ICD9CM_CUI=C0375178&amp;fLockTerm=Unspecified+drug+dependence%2c+unspecified">Unspecified drug dependence, unspecified</a>
 (304.90)                    </div>
